#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/index.rst:5
msgid "Documentation Guidelines"
msgstr "Smernice za dokumentaciju"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/index.rst:7
msgid ""
"QGIS Documentation is available at "
"https://www.qgis.org/resources/hub/#documentation. As the writing process is"
" going on, a build is automatically run every day (see bottom of the page "
"for exact time) for all `supported versions "
"<https://qgis.org/resources/roadmap/#release-schedule>`_ (testing, Long Term"
" Release (LTR) and next-to-be LTR)."
msgstr ""
"Dokumentacija za QGIS je dostupna na "
"https://www.qgis.org/resources/hub/#documentation. Kako proces pisanja "
"traje, izrada se automatski pokreće svakog dana (pogledajte dno stranice za"
" tačno vreme) za sve `podržane verzije "
"<https://qgis.org/resources/roadmap/#release-schedule>`_ (testiranje, "
"dugoročno izdanje (LTR) i buduće LTR)."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/index.rst:12
msgid ""
"QGIS Documentation source files are available at "
"https://github.com/qgis/QGIS-Documentation. They are mainly written using "
"the `reStructuredText (reST) format "
"<https://docutils.sourceforge.io/docs/ref/rst/restructuredtext.html>`_ "
"syntax, coupled with some scripts from the `Sphinx toolset "
"<https://www.sphinx-doc.org/en/master/usage/restructuredtext/basics.html>`_ "
"to post-process the HTML output."
msgstr ""
"Izvorni fajlovi QGIS dokumentacije dostupni su na "
"https://github.com/qgis/QGIS-Documentation. Uglavnom su napisani "
"korišćenjem sintakse formata `reStructuredText (reST) "
"<https://docutils.sourceforge.io/docs/ref/rst/restructuredtext.html>`_, "
"zajedno sa nekim skriptama iz `Sphinx toolset <https://www.sphinx-"
"doc.org/en/master/usage/restructuredtext/basics.html>`_ za naknadnu obradu "
"HTML izlaza."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/index.rst:19
msgid "The following chapters will guide you through learning:"
msgstr "Sledeća poglavlja će vas voditi kroz učenje:"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/index.rst:21
msgid ""
"how to manage the documentation source files using `git <https://git-"
"scm.com/>`_ system and the `GitHub <https://github.com/>`_ platform on which"
" they are stored"
msgstr ""
"kako upravljati izvornim datotekama dokumentacije koristeći `git "
"<https://git-scm.com/>`_ sistem i `GitHub <https://github.com/>`_ platformu "
"na kojoj su smeštene"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/index.rst:23
msgid "how to modify the texts, provide screenshots... in a compliant way"
msgstr ""
"kako izmeniti tekstove, obezbediti snimke ekrana... na način koji je u "
"skladu sa propisima"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/index.rst:24
msgid ""
"how to share and ensure your modifications are pushed to the official docs."
msgstr ""
"kako deliti i osigurati da se vaše izmene objave u zvaničnoj dokumentaciji."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/index.rst:26
msgid ""
"If you are looking for general information about how to contribute to the "
"QGIS project, you may find help at `Get Involved in the QGIS Community "
"<https://qgis.org/community/involve/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ako tražite opšte informacije o tome kako da doprinesete QGIS projektu, "
"pomoć možete pronaći na stranici `Uključite se u QGIS zajednicu "
"<https://qgis.org/community/involve/>`_."
